{"tid":731160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"世界盃球迷 有高達78%的瑞典妹承認自己性慾高漲","createTime":"2018-07-06T03:50:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-07T02:43:50.000Z","uid":72009,"like":18,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"0ea6b1ddf8cb587fb0458d923cd5ecce0efd1462","tid":731160,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T03:50:33.000Z","msg":"報導指出，瑞典妹照片在世足賽比賽期間，有著眾多網友粉絲分享。報導也分析為何瑞典妹深受大家喜愛，其中原因包括瑞典妹比其他歐美女生要來得瘦高，瑞典女生的身高是165公分起跳，而且她們的飲食比其他歐美國家要來得均衡，包括愛吃鮮魚、煮馬鈴薯和越橘。此外，瑞典女生也愛動，雖然瑞典的冬天很漫長，日照也不長，但她們不喜歡坐在沙發，反而喜歡跑步。<br />\n報導更指出，瑞典妹除了又瘦又高，她們也很騷。據去年的一項對性愛態度的統計資料顯示，有高達78%的瑞典妹承認自己性慾高漲。另外有80%瑞典人天生是金髮，也有可能讓金髮控對瑞典妹著迷，而瑞典妹的眼睛，也是全球網友公認最迷人的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180706/1386219\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180706%2F1386219&d=c9KDJrwBTBNzjMKrMG0jmr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=f5f70a49\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180706%2F1386219&h=6b7f93e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180706/1386219</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180706/640_7310aad806c99a2c3c0c17eaaf6ac450.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180706%2F640_7310aad806c99a2c3c0c17eaaf6ac450.jpg&h=56c89e16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180706/640_8511b9b82d5b1f1a74f6512001f3e030.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180706%2F640_8511b9b82d5b1f1a74f6512001f3e030.jpg&h=854b340c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180706/640_7417b1e1cd7d0c9616b83bf8a2792bd1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180706%2F640_7417b1e1cd7d0c9616b83bf8